data.description: Fantastic mountain views from this property. Very quiet North Fork location. 3 bedroom, 2 bath home with open living room and kitchen. Kitchen as double sink, tile counters, double oven, electric cooktop and cozy breakfast nook. Laundry room, 2-car garage, carport, back patio area. 5.21+/- secluded acres with beautiful views. Paved driveway and a shed. Lots of potential here!
